               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17591205-17-off87-c103" targOrder="Y" targets="t17591205-17-defend133 t17591205-17-off87 t17591205-17-verdict89"></join>
         
               <p>18. (M.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17591205-17-defend133" type="defendantName">
                     Mary 
                     Sturger 
                  <interp inst="t17591205-17-defend133" type="surname" value="Sturger"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-defend133" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-defend133" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , <rs id="t17591205-17-deflabel86" type="occupation">widow</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17591205-17-defend133 t17591205-17-deflabel86"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17591205-17-off87" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-off87" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-off87" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing one brass sender, value 2 s. 1 pair of iron tongs, value 6 d. 1 feather pillow, value 12 d. and 1 blanket, value 2 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17591205-17-victim135" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Hopkinson 
                        <interp inst="t17591205-17-victim135" type="surname" value="Hopkinson"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17591205-17-victim135" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17591205-17-victim135" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17591205-17-off87 t17591205-17-victim135"></join>
                     </persName>
                      
                  , the same being in a certain lodging room let by contract
            </rs>, &amp;c, <rs id="t17591205-17-cd88" type="crimeDate">November 27</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17591205-17-off87 t17591205-17-cd88"></join>. ++</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17591205-17-person136">
                  William 
                  Hopkinson 
               <interp inst="t17591205-17-person136" type="surname" value="Hopkinson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-person136" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-person136" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner at the bar came and took a ready furnished room of my wife at 2 s. a week. After she had been in the room the things were missing, so we charged her with taking them, which she owned she had pawned to 
               <persName id="t17591205-17-person137">
                  Mary 
                  Forrest 
               <interp inst="t17591205-17-person137" type="surname" value="Forrest"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-person137" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-person137" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , where I found them. The prisoner in her defence said she did it out of necessity.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17591205-17-verdict89" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-verdict89" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17591205-17-punish90" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-punish90" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17591205-17-punish90" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="branding"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17591205-17-defend133 t17591205-17-punish90"></join>
               
                     <note>[Branding. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
